==Rookie of the Year==
The Rookie of the Year award was given to the conference's best freshman. [[Tom Tumulty]] from Pittsburgh was the first winner. [[Donovan McNabb]], [[Michael Vick]], [[Dion Lewis]], [[Larry Fitzgerald]], and [[Teddy Bridgewater]]<ref name="2012 press release"/> also won Offensive Player of the Year honors, with Vick and Lewis winning both awards in the same season.<ref name="2012 list"/>

